                                <p> The designer creates the look and feel. The developer builds it. The important thing in web design is web should be elegant and clear. </p>
</div> <br>

                <div class="col-md-12 blog-post">
                       <div class="post-title">
                             <a><h1>BASIC</h1></a>
                       </div> 
                                       <ul>
                                       <li> Make the text look professionally designed
                                       <li> Use the power of colors
                                       <li> Get and use amazing images, fonts and icons to make your website shine
                                       <li> Create a layout using whitespace and visual hierarchy
                                       <li> Keep yourself inspired more and more
                                       </ul>
                </div> <br>


                <div class="col-md-12 blog-post">
                       <div class="post-title">
                             <a><h1>TYPOGRAPHY</h1></a>
                       </div> 
                                <p> Typography is the art and technique of arranging type to make written language readable and beautiful. It is essential thing in website, because most websites will be text content. So, it's quite important to make that content good looking and easy to read for the user. A good typography can make every design look very professional</p>
                </div>

